data.description: Beautiful Ranch style home with attractive finished walkout lower level.  Home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, with over 2900 sqft (buyer to verify) living space.  Open great room with custom fireplace, and trey ceilings.  The kitchen features quartz countertops with tile backsplash, stainless appliances, an oversized island bar with recessed sink, plus dining area, walk-in pantry and mud room, 1st floor laundry room located off the kitchen.  The primary suite includes a walk-in closet, large bath with soaking tub, and separate shower.  The lower level is the perfect spot to entertain with a large living area and a 4th bedroom, office, and full bath.  Enjoy the easy access from the walkout to the large backyard, and patio, home also has a deck!
